#taxon[Theorem]
#title[Fundamental Solution of the Pell Equation]

The minimum element of the set
${xi in ZZ[sqrt(D)] | xi > 1, xi overline(xi) = 1}$ is well-defined.
We call this element the _fundamental solution_ of the #local("0030")[Pell equation] and denote it by $epsilon_(D)$.

